    "major_stream_name": "Arts",
    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculty is amazing, they are willing to teach us and always want to help us out. Communicating about attendance issues due to being active in societies is also very easy and they are very supportive",
          "name": "Yamya Jhamb",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "First of all I liked about liberty in choosing elective subjects like other college elective subjects list fills fast in hindu college there is no such criteria",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The alumini network is very strong in this college",
          "name": "Ajay Patle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Another aspect which i love is the infrastructure , the college feels so vibrant and rightfully deserves the no.1 spot , the environment seems to be conducive not only for studies but for the personal growth & the greenery in the campusis so relaxing",
          "name": "Divyanshu",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "My college library is so big that I can study there for the whole day with ease.",
          "name": "Ronak Mathur",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The extra curricular activities of my college are so good that a student get enough opportunities for growth and personality development.",
          "name": "Ronak Mathur",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college administration is very fast, the problems of students gets resolved within a very short period of time.",
          "name": "Ronak Mathur",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Provide lot of opportunities in sports , learning courses and other certificates courses",
          "name": "Prerna",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The clubs are good and I was part of fashion club nakshathra and women development cell.",
          "name": "Pranatha Prajosh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The affordability of the college is very good the fees is very low in comparison to private institutions",
          "name": "Rishabh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I disliked that there is no proper fully vegetarian canteen veg non veg is mix",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus area is very small as it occupied only 25 acres",
          "name": "Ajay Patle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The boys hostel isn't there in the college",
          "name": "Ajay Patle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The parking facilities are not available",
          "name": "Ajay Patle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Provide no specific time for Lunch just continuously classes",
          "name": "Prerna",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lab often lacks apparatus we need and some times sir asks us to bring our own multimeter and all.",
          "name": "Pranatha Prajosh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The focus of the college is more on academics and the opportunities in sports are less",
          "name": "Rishabh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The exposure is good but the placement is not that great in college",
          "name": "Rishabh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Many opportunities like the Research center is not easily accessible.",
          "name": "Imandar Saikia",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The thing I disliked on our college is water scarcity facing seasonally",
          "name": "Shafni banu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Delhi University, New Delhi"
    }
  },
